<div style="background-color:rgba(0,215,0,0.224); color: white; margin:1em;font-family:Times New Roman; padding:5px 10px; text-align:center;"><font size="6">Entrances and Exits</font></div>
===Entrances===         
*In Levels [[Level 9|9]] and [[Level 11|11]], Going inside a school-like building rarely leads here.
*Parts of Level [[Level 52|52]] might seamlessly transfer to this level.
*Noclipping into a locker on Level [[Level 353|353]] will lead to here.
*Having a karma rating of 150 to 199 in Level [[Level 995|995]] will transport here.

===Exits===             
*Exiting the school through the main doors returns the wanderers to their previous level.
*No-clipping in a poster will bring a wanderer to a safe related level as aforementioned above.
*Somehow touching a cloud teleports to either Levels [[Level 399|399's Rosatin Hotel]], [[Level 385|385]], or [[Level 993|993]].
*In rarest cases, an elevator will suddenly appear in front of a wanderer. Entering '''26032009''' in the elevator's codepad will send you to the [[Absolute Infinity of Unknown|Absolute Infinity Of The Unknown]].

